title: 有馬記念の後に・待ちかねた勝利

text_block_list.name: Announcer
text_block_list.text:
And she crosses the finish line in first place,
Matikanetannhauser!
(Whaaaaaaa——!)

text_block_list.name: Matikanetannhauser
text_block_list.text: Hah, hah, hah...!

text_block_list.name: Spectator A
text_block_list.text:
I'm so glad she won...!
Amazing, that was wonderful!

text_block_list.name: Spectator A
text_block_list.text: Thank you for the courage!

text_block_list.name: Spectator B
text_block_list.text:
I'll do my best too...!
Thank you, Machitan!

text_block_list.name: Matikanetannhauser
text_block_list.text: Wah...!

The cheers roar,
enveloping Matikanetannhauser.
On the grass, she looks up at the stands.

text_block_list.name: Matikanetannhauser
text_block_list.text: So many, many, many smiling faces...!

text_block_list.name: Matikanetannhauser
text_block_list.text: (This is what I——)

text_block_list.name: Announcer
text_block_list.text:
Today's star is Matikanetannhauser!
She's dedicated her long-awaited victory to the stands!

text_block_list.name: Matikanetannhauser
text_block_list.text: It's beautiful... Hehe.

text_block_list.name: Matikanetannhauser
text_block_list.text:
Fufun, I won.
Maybe I can brag a little about this?

text_block_list.name: Matikanetannhauser
text_block_list.text: Anyway, today I gotta eat something delicious.

text_block_list.name: Young Umamusume A
text_block_list.text: Machitaaaaan!

text_block_list.name: Matikanetannhauser
text_block_list.text: Whaaa!?

text_block_list.name: Young Umamusume A
text_block_list.text: Congratulatioooons!!

text_block_list.name: Matikanetannhauser
text_block_list.text:
What an energetic Umamusume!
Ah, thank you!!

text_block_list.name: Young Umamusume A
text_block_list.text:
You know, in my club, I'm the slowest, I can't win,
and I have no talent. But, but——

text_block_list.name: Young Umamusume A
text_block_list.text:
I won't lose!
Because Machitan was trying hard too!

text_block_list.name: Young Umamusume A
text_block_list.text:
Thank you!
--See ya!
After saying that, the little Umamusume ran off energetically.

text_block_list.name: Matikanetannhauser
text_block_list.text: Trainer.

text_block_list.name: Matikanetannhauser
text_block_list.text: Right now, I became that kid's 'protagonist,' didn't I?

text_block_list.name: Matikanetannhauser
text_block_list.text:
...Nhehe.
Hehehehe...

text_block_list.name: Matikanetannhauser
text_block_list.text: I'm happy.
Matikanetannhauser watched until the little Umamusume's back disappeared from sight.

text_block_list.name: Matikanetannhauser
text_block_list.text:
Nn...
Alright, let's head back.

text_block_list.name: Matikanetannhauser
text_block_list.text: My racing career is still going on, so I can't be satisfied here, right!

text_block_list.name: Matikanetannhauser
text_block_list.text: Let's keep doing our best from now on too, Trainer!
And so, with new determination, the 'Arima Kinen' came to a close.

text_block_list.name: Matikanetannhauser
text_block_list.text:
...Oh,
I might've left my phone in the waiting room!
